義大利[[方濟各會|方濟各會]][[修士|修士]][[鄂多立克|鄂多立克]]可能在公元1320年前往[[中國|中國]]的途中經過波斯波利斯，但他只提到一座被摧毀的偉大城市，稱其為“Comerum”。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=KorZMqmTOJgC&lpg=PR1&dq=persepolis%20afterlife&pg=PA95#v=onepage&q&f=false|title=Persepolis: Discovery and Afterlife of a World Wonder|last=Mousavi|first=Ali|date=2012-04-19|publisher=Walter de Gruyter|isbn=9781614510338|language=en|access-date=2019-11-10|archive-date=2020-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200518230456/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=KorZMqmTOJgC&lpg=PR1&dq=persepolis%20afterlife&pg=PA95#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>1474年，威尼斯商人[[吉奧索法特·巴爾巴羅|吉奧索法特·巴爾巴羅]]參觀過波斯波利斯的遺跡，他錯把這兒當作猶太人的遺跡。<ref>{{cite book|title=Historical account of discoveries and travels in Asia|first=Hugh|last=Murray|authorlink=Hugh Murray (geographer)|location=Edinburgh|publisher=A. Constable and Co|year=1820|page=15|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=LP4vAAAAYAAJ|access-date=2019-11-10|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410060820/https://books.google.com/books?id=LP4vAAAAYAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>歐洲航海家[[理查德·哈克盧伊特|理查德·哈克盧伊特]]在他的著作“Voyages”中敘述過波斯波利斯遺址的一般情況，資料來自1568年訪問過伊朗的英國商人。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Principal Navigations, Voyages, Traffiques and Discoveries of the English Nation, by Richard Hakluyt : chapter11|url=https://ebooks.adelaide.edu.au/h/hakluyt/voyages/v04/chapter11.html|website=ebooks.adelaide.edu.au|access-date=2019-07-03|archive-date=2019-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190703223548/https://ebooks.adelaide.edu.au/h/hakluyt/voyages/v04/chapter11.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/?id=cwFPDgAAQBAJ&pg=PR3&dq=persian+responses#v=onepage&q&f=false|title=Persian Responses: Political and Cultural Interaction with(in) the Achaemenid Empire|last=Tuplin|first=Christopher|date=2007-12-31|publisher=ISD LLC|isbn=9781910589465|language=en}}</ref>來自葡萄牙的{{link-en|安東尼奧·古韋維亞|António de Gouveia}}在1602年訪問當地之後提及[[楔形文字|楔形文字]]。他對波斯波利斯遺址的記錄在1611年出版的作品《Relaçam》裡面出現過。

1618年，西班牙國王[[腓力三世_(西班牙)|腓力三世]]在[[薩菲王朝|薩菲王朝]]的[[阿拔斯一世_(波斯)|阿拔斯一世]]時期，派任到伊朗的大使{{link-en|加西亞·席爾瓦 菲格羅亞|Garcíade Silva Figueroa}}，是第一個西方人把伊朗人稱為“Chehel Minar”的地點，與古典作家稱為波斯波利斯的地點聯繫起來的人。<ref>{{cite book|title=Road to Babylon: Development of U.S. Assyriology|author=C. Wade Meade|publisher=Brill Archive|year=1974|pages=5–7|url=https://books.google.com/?id=iuAUAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA5&dq=Garc%C3%ADa+de+Silva+Figueroa+persepolis#v=onepage&q=Garc%C3%ADa%20de%20Silva%20Figueroa%20persepolis&f=false|isbn=978-9004038585|access-date=2019-11-10|archive-date=2019-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913093627/https://books.google.com/books?id=iuAUAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA5&dq=Garc%C3%ADa+de+Silva+Figueroa+persepolis&hl=en#v=onepage&q=Garc%C3%ADa%20de%20Silva%20Figueroa%20persepolis&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>

義大利作曲家兼作家{{link-en|彼得羅·德拉·瓦勒|Pietro Della Valle}}於1621年訪問過波斯波利斯，並注意到由於故意破壞或自然風化過程，原來的72根柱子中只剩25根仍然矗立。<ref>{{cite book|title=تخت جمشيد (Persepolis)|author=M. H. Aminisam|publisher=AuthorHouse|year=2007|pages=79–81|url=https://books.google.com/?id=LrS6d-vvCcUC&pg=PA80&dq=Pietro+della+Valle+persepolis#v=onepage&q=Pietro%20della%20Valle%20persepolis&f=false|isbn=9781463462529|access-date=2019-11-10|archive-date=2019-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913093621/https://books.google.com/books?id=LrS6d-vvCcUC&pg=PA80&dq=Pietro+della+Valle+persepolis&hl=en#v=onepage&q=Pietro%20della%20Valle%20persepolis&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>荷蘭旅行者{{link-en|科尼里斯 布魯因|Cornelis de Bruijn}}於1704年訪問過波斯波利斯。<ref>{{cite book|title=Persepolis: Discovery and Afterlife of a World Wonder|author=Ali Mousavi|publisher=Walter de Gruyter|year=2012|pages=104–7|url=https://books.google.com/?id=p585AgAAQBAJ&pg=PA106&dq=Cornelis+de+Bruijn+persepolis#v=onepage&q=Cornelis%20de%20Bruijn%20persepolis&f=false|isbn=9781614510284|access-date=2019-11-10|archive-date=2019-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913093557/https://books.google.com/books?id=p585AgAAQBAJ&pg=PA106&dq=Cornelis+de+Bruijn+persepolis&hl=en#v=onepage&q=Cornelis%20de%20Bruijn%20persepolis&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>

